metadata.name: Crypto Kangaroo Lootbox
metadata.description:
Crypto Kangaroos are from the Nabox community, as loyal supporters, we want to contribute our parts in the future development of Nabox and WEB 3.  
 From Genesis kangaroo : “We are kangaroos from the Nabox planet, we store your data in our chest pocket and we will guard your information in a safe place!”  
 There are 200 sets of series in the Crypto Kangaroos NFTs. In every set there are 10 different kangaroo NFTs with their hands holding different Cryptos (BTC  ETH  BNB ADA LUNA SOL AVAX  UNI  MATIC NABOX). The total release amount of kangaroo NFTs is very limited and rare - 2000 pieces , and we will not release other similar NFTs in the future.
